      "x": 110,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 1020,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "1. Manual Trigger / Schedule  →  2. Google Drive (Source Docs)  →  3. Extract from File  →  4. RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter (chunk ~500-1000 tokens)  →  5. OpenAI Embeddings (text-embedding-3-small)  →  6. Pinecone Upsert (3 Namespaces: marketing, projects, faq)",
