      "x": 110,
      "y": 955,
      "width": 1020,
      "height": 90,
      "text": "🎯 Pattern: RAG-as-a-Tool  •  Ingestion pipeline runs independently (scheduled/manual)  •  Retrieval exposed as LangChain Tool (VectorStoreTool)  •  Any agent can query via tool interface — no direct coupling  •  Namespace segregation prevents cross-contamination  •  Same Pinecone index, different namespaces for different domains  •  Embedding model: text-embedding-3-small (consistent across ingestion + query)",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#92400e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "originalText": "🎯 Pattern: RAG-as-a-Tool  •  Ingestion pipeline runs independently (scheduled/manual)  •  Retrieval exposed as LangChain Tool (VectorStoreTool)  •  Any agent can query via tool interface — no direct coupling  •  Namespace segregation prevents cross-contamination  •  Same Pinecone index, different namespaces for different domains  •  Embedding model: text-embedding-3-small (consistent across ingestion + query)",
      "autoResize": true
    },
